      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical R2022 is a commercially validated FEA solver with documented QA procedures, regression test suites, and ISO 9001-certified development process. All simulation scripts version-controlled in institutional repository with audit trail. Achieved level 3 exceeds the required level 2 for a medium model-risk application."
